<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WONDERFUL WORDS OF LIFE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zaila'n ka kiengah sakit in,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh!
 A hawihnau chu ei muhsak in,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh!
 Hinna leh hawihna thu,
 A gin dan ei hilh in!

[V2]
 * Thu hawihtak chuh, thu maktak chuh!
 Hinna thu maktak chuh! (2)

[V3]
 2. Mi cheng kiengah Krista'n A piei,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh;
 Gilo lungsiet sapna ngaiin,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh!
 Man beia piek I hiu,
 Van gam I tun theihna'n!

[V4]
 3. Gospel sapna'n gamtin athawng,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh!
 Ngaihdam, muonna micheng A piei,
 Hinna thu maktak chuh;
 Isu mai Hukdampa,
 Kumkhuo'n A hih thiengtho.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>225</hymn_number>
</song>